  * * * * * * * *     EDMODE ISPF/PDF EDIT command    * * * * * * * *
  * * * * * * * *                                     * * * * * * * *
  * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * *

  Function :   This Edit macro may be used to verify and set the EDIT
  ----------   modes for the current edit file.

  Command syntax : EDMODE
  ---------------- EDMODE HELP or H

  Use :        Type EDMODE on the COMMAND line, and you will be
  -----        prompted to verify and eventually change the EDIT modes
               for the data you are currently editing.
               The EDIT modes you may control are :
                   STATS               NUMBER              AUTONUM
                   VERSION/LEVEL       NULLS               AUTOLIST
                   RECOVERY            HEX                 AUTOSAVE
                   CAPS                BOUNDS
